---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Burdweiser.com" description="About James Burd — infrastructure engineer based in Houston, TX.">
  <div class="container page-wrap">
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="page-eyebrow">about</div>
      <h1>James Burd</h1>
      <p class="page-sub">Infrastructure Engineer · Houston, TX</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content prose">
      <p>
        I'm an infrastructure engineer based in Houston, TX with hands-on experience designing,
        deploying, and operating enterprise virtualization, Kubernetes, and AI/ML infrastructure.
        This site is where I document what I learn — sometimes from official documentation,
        more often from things breaking at 2am.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Write About</h2>
      <p>The focus areas here are the things I work with day to day:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>VMware / Broadcom VCF</strong> — vSphere, NSX-T, vSAN, and the ongoing saga of the Broadcom acquisition</li>
        <li><strong>NVIDIA Data Center</strong> — GPU architecture, DGX systems, NVLink, and enterprise AI compute</li>
        <li><strong>Kubernetes</strong> — cluster operations, GitOps, Helm, Argo CD, Cilium, and the surrounding ecosystem</li>
        <li><strong>AI Infrastructure</strong> — LLM deployment, inference optimization, MLOps, and running models locally</li>
        <li><strong>Homelab</strong> — self-hosted tooling, TrueNAS, Proxmox, and Docker stacks</li>
        <li><strong>Networking</strong> — SDN, BGP, VLANs, Tailscale, and data center fabric design</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Certifications</h2>
      <p>
        My verified certifications are published on Credly. You can view and verify badges at:
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="https://www.credly.com/users/james-burd" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ext-link">
          credly.com/users/james-burd →
        </a>
      </p>

      <h2>Connect</h2>
      <p>The best way to reach me or follow my work:</p>
      <ul class="connect-list">
        <li>
          <span class="connect-label">LinkedIn</span>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/james-burd-7602414/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            linkedin.com/in/james-burd-7602414
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="connect-label">Credly</span>
          <a href="https://www.credly.com/users/james-burd" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            credly.com/users/james-burd
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="connect-label">GitHub</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/burdweiser" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            github.com/burdweiser
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="connect-label">RSS</span>
          <a href="/rss.xml">
            burdweiser.com/rss.xml
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>About This Site</h2>
      <p>
        Burdweiser.com is built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>,
        hosted on <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Pages</a>,
        and deployed automatically from a GitHub repository. Content is written in Markdown.
      </p>
      <p>
        The name is a play on my last name — and a reminder that good infrastructure decisions,
        like good beer, should be made deliberately and consumed responsibly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-wrap { padding-top: 0; max-width: 720px; }
  .page-header {
    padding: 48px 0 36px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .page-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .page-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .content { padding-bottom: 64px; }
  strong { font-weight: 500; color: var(--text); }

  .ext-link {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .connect-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  }
  .connect-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .connect-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text3);
    min-width: 64px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .connect-list a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    word-break: break-all;
  }
</style>
